data.description: Adorable 3BR/2BA expanded cottage located on a spacious lot in the quiet neighborhood of Essex.  Pull into the double wide driveway, make your way to the cozy covered front porch,  and open the door into your forever home. Step inside to an open floor plan with an eclectic design beginning in the spacious living room and leading into the large kitchen.  The kitchen offers plenty of counter space with gray lower cabinets and white uppers finished with crown moldings, a beautiful tiled backsplash, and stainless steel appliances.  Beyond the kitchen is one of two primary sized bedrooms and a full bath.  Down the hall are the two remaining bedrooms, a sizable secondary, a spacious primary, and a full bath.  The lower has tons of possibilities with one finished room ideal for office space, laundry, storage, and a walk-out to the fenced side yard.  Step out onto a wood deck that overlooks tons of green space in the sprawling yard ideal when hosting family gatherings.  This home is perfect for the new homeowner and is located in close proximity to shopping, restaurants, and commuter routes.
